<div id="content-after-image">
<section class="content-wrapper">
<div class="box contrast less-space verdict">
<div class="sub-box full">
<h3>Our Verdict</h3>
<p>The Nvidia Shield TV (2019) offers seamless game-streaming, fast-loading 4K HDR content and ambitious AI upscaling for 1080p video.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="box contrast less-space pro-con">
<div class="sub-box">
<h4 class="icon icon-plus_circle">
For
</h4>
<ul>
<li>
Excellent game-streaming
</li>
<li>
Quick rendering of UHD content
</li>
<li>
Lots of great apps
</li>
<li>
Attractive new design
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="sub-box">
<h4 class="icon icon-minus_circle">
Against
</h4>
<ul>
<li>
AI upscaling doesn't add that much
</li>
<li>
Somewhat expensive
</li>
</ul>
</div>
